{
  "text": "The LSER model values showed a good regression of the experimental data for all investigated systems. The temperature susceptibility coefficient, d, shows that all the systems in references [CITATION_1] are temperature sensitive.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "95243013"
